Dear Applicant,

I have examined the above application. There is an objection under section
3(1)(b) and (c) of the Trade Marks Act 1994. The mark NORTHWIND SOLAR is
descriptive of the goods in class 9 (solar panels) and is devoid of
distinctive character.

You have a period of two months from the date of this report, expiring on
11 August 2026, to file written observations or request a hearing. If no
response is received the application will be treated as withdrawn.

Application number: UK00003999000

